mint.t.sol
├── when caller is not minter
│   └── it should revert with CallerNotMinter
└── when caller is minter
    ├── when recipient is not zero address
    │   ├── when amount is greater than 0
    │   │   ├── it should mint tokens to the specified address
    │   │   ├── it should increase the total supply
    │   │   └── it should emit a Transfer event
    │   └── when amount is 0
    │       ├── it should not change recipient balance
    │       ├── it should not change total supply
    │       └── it should emit a Transfer event with 0 amount
    └── when recipient is zero address
        └── it should revert with "ERC20: mint to the zero address"
